[normal]20/3/00
[normal] reported that David Parker
[normal] of the Met Office’s 
[normal]Hadley Centre 
[normal]forecast that “
[normal]British children could have only virtual experience of snow. Via the internet, they might wonder at polar scenes - or eventually "feel" virtual cold.
