[normal] The Met Office produced UK Climate Projections 2009 which purports to project “how the 
[normal]UK
[normal] climate may change for the 30 year period from 2010-2099 at a resolution of 25km.” 
[normal]C
[normal]limatologist 
[normal]Professor Emeritus 
[normal]R.A. Piel
[normal]ke Sr. of the 
[normal]U
[normal]niversity
[normal] of 
[normal]Colorado
